Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Abortion law thunderbolt
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0441y42
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 9 Jul 1989
Abortion arguments will continue to rage as Supreme Court fudges the issue and hands back control to states. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less